{"tid":1641350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山新港城商場今晚七點閂門","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:36:47.000Z","uid":199911,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3ff7432433dedd07895a1f9718c167699fc391","tid":1641350,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:11.000Z","msg":"From MOSTown Management:<br />\n<br />\nWe are aware of potential large-scale public event on MOSTown. For the safety of tenants and customers, MOSTown is closed on 19:00, 9 October. If any assistance is needed, please contact our staff at 2631 0334. We apologize for any inconvenience caused.<br />\n<br />\n新港城中心商場管理處示<br />\n留意到新港城中心可能會出現大型公眾活動，為顧及商戶及顧客的安全，新港城中心商場於10月9日7時正暫停營業。各商戶如需協助，請致電2631 0334與管理處職員聯絡。不便之處，敬請原諒。"},{"pid":"26e597a7c632362dc4dbd91e77e8718ac8a21a21","tid":1641350,"uid":23256,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"姐係玩野啦 明知人支持保安"},{"pid":"d1b9f96abbbd4cf83f2846f4d6a069f1407a69ec","tid":1641350,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"上！"},{"pid":"8e11aa6ab64e23f88ce2437b87465035bed124a9","tid":1641350,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"c1cf4e4002f586e918fab9ed9d65ae77c5169adb","tid":1641350,"uid":69741,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"26e597a7c632362dc4dbd91e77e8718ac8a21a21","tid":1641350,"uid":23256,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"姐係玩野啦 明知人支持保安"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:17:02.000Z","msg":"港鐵8點就唔開，新城市都拉閘啦，何況呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都要幫鋪頭d人都要放工架"},{"pid":"ec51fbaa8d3485fe2f1b03506d293bd764f50d29","tid":1641350,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"大家小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk